data.description: Welcome to this move in ready, sweet expansion bungalow, in this quiet Lester Park neighborhood. Greet your guests into this beautiful living room with hardwood floor, large west facing window and closet for the coats. The kitchen has plenty of cupboards, and a nice place for a table next to the south facing bay window overlooking the deck. The home has 2 large main floor bedrooms, both with large double door closets and hardwood floors, and full main floor bath with lots of storage, and a hall closet as well. Upstairs is a large bedroom fully carpeted with double door closet, storage, skylight and windows with blinds on both ends, and very well insulated. The lower level has a rec. room with built-in cupboards, countertop and shelves. The laundry room is large and has a wall of built-in shelves for lots of storage. Don’t miss the workshop with bench, pegboard, and two windows. This corner lot has no alley so less traffic, large Apple, Birch and Pine trees, also gardens including Hydrangea Bush, Hosta, Corn Flower, Black Eye Susan, Bleeding Heart and Ferns for you to enjoy while relaxing on your cozy southside deck. There is a motion sensor light over the deck, lighting the way between the back door and the garage, and another on northeast corner of home. Furnace 2013, Washer and Dryer 2023. newer efficient water heater.  All appliances and window coverings are included. *Agent is related to seller.
